{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_149","type":"agent_message","text":"Implemented the Milestone 15 suite planner end to end.\n\nThe main addition is a canonical planner API in [experiment_suite_planning.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/src/flywire_wave/experiment_suite_planning.py#L259) and [experiment_suite_planning.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/src/flywire_wave/experiment_suite_planning.py#L301). `normalize_experiment_suite_config(...)` now normalizes local suite defaults, and `resolve_experiment_suite_plan(...)` resolves either a suite manifest or an experiment manifest with an embedded `suite` block into one deterministic orchestration surface. The returned plan records active dimensions, sweep axes, cross-product vs linked expansion, seed reuse policy, ablation declarations, comparison pairings, stage targets, output roots, and stable suite/work-item/artifact ordering while reusing the existing simulation/readout-analysis planning layers rather than bypassing them. Clear failures were added for unknown dimensions, linked-axis mismatches, unsupported ablation variants, contradictory perturbation seed rules, missing subset prerequisites, and unsupported wave-dependent requests.\n\nI also added the suite output-root config default in [config.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/src/flywire_wave/config.py#L14), exported the new module in [__init__.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/src/flywire_wave/__init__.py#L3), extended the shared simulation fixture helper to accept `experiment_suite` config in [test_simulation_planning.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/tests/test_simulation_planning.py#L931), added focused regression coverage in [test_experiment_suite_planning.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/tests/test_experiment_suite_planning.py#L48), and wrote the required rationale note at [FW-M15-002_rationale.md](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/docs/experiment_orchestration_notes/FW-M15-002_rationale.md#L1).\n\nVerified with `./.venv/bin/python -m unittest discover -s tests -p 'test_experiment_suite_planning.py' -v` and `make test`. Full suite result: `Ran 224 tests in 182.733s` and `OK`."}}
